<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="uz">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>5-Maktab</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial;
      background: #f4f4f4;
      margin: 0;
    }

    header {
      background: #2c3e50;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }

    .container {
      display: flex;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    }

    .container img {
      width: 400px;
      object-fit: cover;
    }

    .info {
      padding: 20px;
    }

    .info h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    .info p {
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .info ul {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .info li {
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>5-Maktab</header>

<div class="container">
  <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1580587771525-78b9dba3b914" alt="Maktab rasmi">
  <div class="info">
    <h2>5-Maktab haqida</h2>
    <p>5-maktab — bu zamonaviy ta’lim beruvchi maktablardan biri bo‘lib, o‘quvchilarga sifatli bilim va tarbiya beradi. Bu yerda tajribali o‘qituvchilar faoliyat yuritadi.</p>

    <ul>
      <li>🏫 Manzil: Taxtakopir rayoninda jaylasqan jaylashgan</li>
      <li>👨‍🏫 Tajziybeli o‘qituvchilar</li>
      <li>📚 Zamanavoy Sabaqlarlar</li>
      <li>💻 Kompyuter xonasi bar</li>
      <li>⚽ Sport maydani bor</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
